Files are .mp4 

Avoid these types of files as most are just containers for bad rips. AVI is always just what they say to be so look for those instead. Some mp4 do contain good codec use but it's extremely rare.

Thanks to the uploader for making it clear in this instance that the encoding is odd ... will not play well on most computers, specially not cpu machines that are not brand new as of 2011
